notes_display: Medal commemorates the Great Siege of Gibraltar.  On obverse, between words SOCIVS and NON, there is a very thin question mark.  Medal is composed of white metal with a copper plug.
issue_obverse_figure_description_s: bust of General Eliott wearing cocked hat.
issue_obverse_legend_s: ELLIOT AN MARTIS SOCIVS NON : IVPITER IPSE EST
issue_reverse_figure_description_s: Scene depicting action with Spanish batteries and ships in foreground.
issue_reverse_legend_s: VICTRIX IN FLAMIS VICTRIX GIBRALTAR IN VNDIS (Gibraltar victorious alike amid flames and through waves).
